claim.claim-text:
1. A substrate for forming a mask comprising:
a substantially light transparent substrate;
a phase shifting layer disposed over said substantially light transparent substrate;
a substantially light shielding layer disposed over said phase shifting layer; and,
at least one barrier layer disposed over said substantially light shielding layer, wherein said at least one barrier layer comprises a hardmask disposed over an anti-reflective coating (ARC) layer, and each barrier layer of said at least one barrier layer does not comprise a Cr-based layer.
